{
  "id": "5dbe97e51b8ef30017ab57ae",
  "title": "暗号通貨とブロックチェーン",
  "created": 1572771815,
  "updated": 1572786401,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5dbe97e51b8ef30017ab57ae",
      "text": "暗号通貨とブロックチェーン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771815,
      "updated": 1572771815
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe97e7aff09e0000420465",
      "text": "[/mkk/5. 10月17日 暗号通貨とブロックチェーン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771815,
      "updated": 1572771856
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe980faff09e0000420466",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771856,
      "updated": 1572771856
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe982caff09e0000420467",
      "text": "\t電子現金",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771885,
      "updated": 1572771887
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9833aff09e0000420469",
      "text": "\t\t日本では1996年に日銀とNTTが研究していた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771891,
      "updated": 1572771901
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe983caff09e000042046a",
      "text": "\t[現金の匿名性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771901,
      "updated": 1572771922
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe982faff09e0000420468",
      "text": "\t\tキャッシュレス→お金の追跡が容易に",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771887,
      "updated": 1572771935
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe985eaff09e000042046c",
      "text": "\t\tメリット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771935,
      "updated": 1572771940
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9864aff09e000042046d",
      "text": "\t\t\t脱税やマネーロンダリングが困難に",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771941,
      "updated": 1572771950
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe986daff09e000042046e",
      "text": "\t\tデメリット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771950,
      "updated": 1572771951
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9870aff09e000042046f",
      "text": "\t\t\tお金を何に使ったのか監視できる→プライバシーの問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771953,
      "updated": 1572771966
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe987eaff09e0000420470",
      "text": "\tSuica",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771966,
      "updated": 1572771976
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9888aff09e0000420471",
      "text": "\t\t集中サーバで処理",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771976,
      "updated": 1572771987
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9892aff09e0000420472",
      "text": "\t⇔[Bitcoin]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771987,
      "updated": 1572772437
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe98a7aff09e0000420474",
      "text": "\t\t[非集中的]([decentralized])に[二重使用]([double-spending])を防止した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772007,
      "updated": 1572772085
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe98f4aff09e0000420475",
      "text": "\t\tデータは基本的に複製が容易",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772085,
      "updated": 1572772092
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe98fbaff09e0000420476",
      "text": "\t\t現金のような目的に使う場合にコピーして複数回使われると困る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772092,
      "updated": 1572772109
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe990daff09e0000420477",
      "text": "\t\t非集中的であることを[トラストレス]とも言う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772109,
      "updated": 1572772240
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9896aff09e0000420473",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771990,
      "updated": 1572771990
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9856aff09e000042046b",
      "text": "\tトラストレス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572771926,
      "updated": 1572772281
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe99b9aff09e0000420479",
      "text": "\t\tSuicaはSuicaのサーバが信頼できることが前提のシステム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772281,
      "updated": 1572772293
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe99c4aff09e000042047a",
      "text": "\t\tBitcoinはノード全体の2/3が悪意のないノードであれば問題なく動く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772293,
      "updated": 1572772335
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe99efaff09e000042047b",
      "text": "\t\t今1万弱のノードがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772335,
      "updated": 1572772383
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9a1faff09e000042047c",
      "text": "\t\t\t中国は3%程度",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772383,
      "updated": 1572772391
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9a20aff09e000042047d",
      "text": "\t\t\t[nishio.icon]てっきり過半数ぐらい中国なのかと思っていた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772385,
      "updated": 1572772401
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9a31aff09e000042047e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772401,
      "updated": 1572772407
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9a41aff09e000042047f",
      "text": "\tBitcoinの仕組みから、お金の部分を取り除いたものが[ブロックチェーン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772418,
      "updated": 1572772433
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe99b8aff09e0000420478",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772281,
      "updated": 1572772281
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9aa1aff09e0000420481",
      "text": "\t乱高下していると決済手段として使いづらい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772514,
      "updated": 1572772522
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9aa9aff09e0000420483",
      "text": "\t\t現実の通貨と連動させる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772522,
      "updated": 1572772564
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ad3aff09e0000420484",
      "text": "\t\t関連: [ドルペッグ制 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%89%E3%83%AB%E3%83%9A%E3%83%83%E3%82%B0%E5%88%B6]  #ドルペッグ制",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772564,
      "updated": 1572772578
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ae2aff09e0000420485",
      "text": "\t\tどうやって実現するのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772579,
      "updated": 1572772596
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9afeaff09e0000420486",
      "text": "\t\t\t素朴な方法=通貨発行額と同額のドルを預金しておいて要求に応じて交換する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772606,
      "updated": 1572772764
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9b9caff09e0000420487",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「同額のドルを預金」が現実的でない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772765,
      "updated": 1572772778
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ba9aff09e0000420488",
      "text": "\t\t\tシニョリッジシェアシステム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772778,
      "updated": 1572772789
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9bb4aff09e0000420489",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[シニョリッジ - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%B7%E3%83%8B%E3%83%A7%E3%83%AA%E3%83%83%E3%82%B8]  #シニョリッジ #通貨発行益",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772789,
      "updated": 1572772819
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9aa6aff09e0000420482",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t価格が高くなるとコイン供給量が増える仕組み",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772518,
      "updated": 1572772909
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9c4aaff09e000042049c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t余剰の供給を売却することで現金を得る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772938,
      "updated": 1572772966
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9c7faff09e000042049d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\tコインXが価格1ドルを維持したい場合、価格が2ドルになった時にはXを売って2ドルを得る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572772991,
      "updated": 1572773023
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ce5aff09e00004204a2",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\tこの現金は貯めておく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773093,
      "updated": 1572773100
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9cfbaff09e00004204a3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\tこれを[シニョリッジ利潤]と呼ぶ？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773115,
      "updated": 1572773137
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9cb0aff09e000042049f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t価格が安くなった時には市場からコインを購入する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773041,
      "updated": 1572773060
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ce3aff09e00004204a1",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t先ほど貯めておいた現金を使う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773091,
      "updated": 1572773147
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9d29aff09e00004204a6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tこの現金が尽きている場合買うことができない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773162,
      "updated": 1572773178
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9d3baff09e00004204a7",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t>この場合、将来の利潤で償還することを約束してシニョリッジ・シェアを発行することで対処します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773180,
      "updated": 1572773313
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9d28aff09e00004204a5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t[ステーブルコイン（Stablecoin）とは https://blog.liquid.com/ja/insight/what-is-stablecoin-190510]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773160,
      "updated": 1572773350
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9de5aff09e00004204a8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t「将来増えて戻ってくる」と信じてシェアを買う人がいなければ維持できないシステム",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773350,
      "updated": 1572773378
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9e21aff09e00004204aa",
      "text": "\t\tFacebookの[Libra]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773409,
      "updated": 1572773420
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9deaaff09e00004204a9",
      "text": "\t\t\t通貨バスケットに対してペッグする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773354,
      "updated": 1572773428
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9e31aff09e00004204ab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773426,
      "updated": 1572773426
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9e6baff09e00004204ac",
      "text": "\t[Web3]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773484,
      "updated": 1572773488
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9e6daff09e00004204ad",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/57988cf4439dbfff4ce03df814d32f1e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773486,
      "updated": 1572773538
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ea2aff09e000075169c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773538,
      "updated": 1572773538
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbe9ea2aff09e000075169b",
      "text": "\t\t関連: [個人所有グループウェア]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572773538,
      "updated": 1572786401
    },
    {
      "id": "5dbed0daaff09e0000dfd731",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1572786395,
      "updated": 1572786395
    }
  ]
}